3.19.3
===

- Add visual feedback for invisible characters (bug#757815)
- Rework search function to feed more results when the user scrolls
  the list to the bottom (bug#757523)
- Standardize app menu
- Disable search provider by default
- Add notification for clipboard access (bug#755212)
- Switch away from gnome-autogen.sh

