3.15.90
===

- Support character filtering by font
- Bundle Gnulib libunistring modules to provide Unicode 7.0.0 support,
  which will be compiled in only when the system libunistring is < 0.9.5
- Bug 740260 - Emoticons section - characters are cut off at the bottom
- Bug 744331 - Don't default to recently used when it is empty
- Bug 744479 - Unicode text should be selectable

